528
00:29:44,540 --> 00:29:45,380
How about this?

529
00:29:45,990 --> 00:29:46,990
Stay at my place tonight.

530
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,950
You can go home
when your mom cools down.

531
00:29:49,410 --> 00:29:50,830
Perhaps at my place.

532
00:29:51,080 --> 00:29:52,450
We can talk a lot.

533
00:29:52,580 --> 00:29:54,330
Besides, my parents are not at home.

534
00:29:54,580 --> 00:29:55,740
You'll be more at ease.

535
00:29:56,740 --> 00:29:57,700
Her parents went out,

536
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:58,910
