00:30:12,310 --> 00:30:13,180
Shasha,

547
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,870
you haven't been
this happy for a long time.

548
00:30:15,580 --> 00:30:18,240
Come on, let's take a selfie.

549
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,080
Okay.

550
00:30:23,700 --> 00:30:25,290
Niannian, promise me

551
00:30:25,620 --> 00:30:26,660
you won't

552
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:28,830
